\[F_{\lambda}\left(h,\mathbf{X}\right)=\lambda\left(h\right)\Delta\left(h, \mathbf{X}\right)-\frac{\lambda\left(h\right)^{2}}{1-\lambda\left(h\right)/n }\frac{v\left(h\right)}{n}.\]

