\[\ln\mathbb{E}_{\mathbf{X}}\left[\mathbb{E}_{h\sim Q_{\mathbf{X}}}\left[e^{F_{ \lambda}\left(h,\mathbf{X}\right)}\right]\right]\leq\frac{3}{\sigma^{2}} \mathcal{V}\left(A\right),\]

